%% Smart city twin and energy grid twin provide:
%% - Runtime instance data
%% - Schema/ontology context
%% - Relationship topology

%% Transformation layer:
%% - Is a software pipeline
%% - Produces normalized, validated decision-ready objects
%% - Enforces units, time semantics, identity, and data quality
%%   - This is the stable decision contract.

%% Decision service:
%% - Runs feasibility checks and constraint reasoning
%% - Produces decision candidates and explanations
%% - Hands off to planning/execution downstream (out of scope now)

